    <h2>Ready to Remediate Your Vulnerabilities?</h2>
    <p>Sheepdog Cyber Defense helps you develop realistic remediation plans and supports you through the entire process. Contact us for guidance on your penetration test findings.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Let's Talk Remediation</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

